latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The smile on the faces of people in this video, when they are asked to break down the box of biases, shows how liberating even a small act makes them feel. 
Imagine how much happiness the rest of you could bring into our LGBTQAI+ community just by keeping insensitivity aside. 

This beautiful video sets a correct example. I am so proud to see Future Generali team, standing as a strong ally with the #pride community by being an inclusive employer.

Viva Las Vegas babyyyyy !!!!! 

Part two - photo and video collage. 

The amount of fun I have had in Las Vegas cannnnot be measured !!! 

Dropping a little Indian magic wherever I go ! 

I’ve always wanted to travel to North America but explore all these beautiful places and now I actually get to do it in real time ! 

To add to that I get to do it with people I absolutely love. 

Meeting so many wonderful people along the way !!! 
Yaaassss. 

NamaSLAYYYYY babyyyy !!! 
P.S- I never thought I’d be roaming around in Cadillacs and limos but the human mind is surprised every day !!! 

#america #vegas #vegasbaby #vegasstrip #vegasvacation #vegasready #lasvegas #queer #trans #transgender #genderfluid #lgbt #lgbtq #namaslay #rani #ranikohenur

How beautiful is it that today happens to be international Mothers Day as welllll as my dad’s birthday !!! 

Amidst all the craziness before I leave for my debut to represent India at @rupaulsdragcon ,
The thing that has constantly been with me is my parents’ love ! 

My mother has been , is and will always be the reason our family is a family ! 

She has taught me grace , sass , strength and courage of conviction ! 
Nothing is impossible if you set your heart and mind to it ! 
Mumma has taught me to be fearless and embrace my authentic self ! 

Through her beautiful parenting , I have vicariously learned motherhood in all its glory and to further give the same love to my children ! 

To all the wonderful mothers around the world , you are not to be celebrated just this one day , but every dayyyyyyy ♥️♥️♥️♥️. 

#mothersday #mom #momlife #momlove #family #fam #instagood

Hi Mommy @sushantdivgikr ! 🙏 #GungunaLe 

Cajon and U-bass by @kalabrandmusic 
Shot and edited by @saketsamudre 
Mixed and mastered by @biplabphukan
Arrangement by @antara_nandy

Default settings ><advanced settings. 

Riyaaz ka kamaal 

Retaining the original vocal dexterity , strengthening multiple octaves , adding new vocal flavours to the voice is my favourite pass time. ❤️❤️❤️. 

1…..2…..3……. RIYAAAAAAZZZZZZ !!! 

This wonderful show for @futuregenerali @generaligroup had me all excited and I wanted to give a tribute to @sunidhichauhan5 and @usha.uthup so I wore a saree with the Gajaras and sang one of favvvvv Sunidhi ma’am songs ! 

🎵Mehboob mere , Mehboob mere ,
Tere aankhon se mujhe peene de ,
Kuch dard hai mere seene mein !
Mujhe mast mahaul mein jeene de 🎵 

What an absolute banger of a song composed by @anumalikmusic sir and written by Tejpal Kaur ! 

Here’s to many many more moments like this in 2024 ❤️❤️🫶🏼🫶🏼🫰🏼🫰🏼. 

Make up and beauty director - @addyartistry 
Hair artistry @_raziea 
Nails @umikasnailsandmore 
Saree is a gift from @saiganesh_krishnamoorthy 🫶🏼❤️ 

Special thanks to @nishithhegde and @mayankshawarma for accompanying me on stage and giving such great orchestration realness !!!

latestPosts.caption:
NamaSLEIGH 🧑‍🎄 and a very Merry Christmas to everyone . 

This Christmas I was my own Santa ! 
Gifted myself a new phone AND even though my health is not at its best , I did one of my most power packed LIVE shows in Goa ! 

SHE LOVES TO MAKE THAT COINNNNNNN 💰 and work hard for it ! 

I am SO SOOOO PROUD of never giving up ! A trait I have gotten from my parents ! 

Here’s to celebrating a very very eventful year and looking forward for what 2025 has in store. 

The KoHEnur is readyyyyy to NamaSLEIGH 🛷 !!
